Package DataBase

Class DataBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataBase.DataBase

  • public class DataBase
extends java.lang.Object
    The class contains database object- which contains information stored in two sets of Samples.
    one set is for all the receiving info and the other is for storing the filtered info.
    the object also contains hashmap that store samples according to macs. The class contains some functions: add, removeall, starthash, updatehash
